title: The Chemist v0.1.05
description: In The Chemist, working hard and managing your resources well is as important as making the right decisions about your life and your work. Making the best out of the contracts and the resources available to you, youl find yourself creating recipes for all sorts of different liquids and finding answers to your questions like hat would happen if my fruit soda could also be used as a soap?.
